text: Be careful riding the Mandai Trail. It can be treacherous and slippery with sharp stones. Not for the inexperienced MTB rider.
The first shelter you will see if you coming from Bangkit HDB. Mostly use by cyclists and also hikers as rest area.
This is resting place, you will see mostly hikers and mountain bikers here.
This is a shelter within Chestnut National Park. This is a shelter for both hikers and bikers, and it is large.
